These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Birthday   | october | january | december | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, chaman, oliveros, game
1. the game-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the game-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the swisher-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | chaman | game | swisher | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, tomato, lemon, orange
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the person eating tomato and the person eating orange##2
3. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | spinach | orange | lemon | tomato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy, adventure, horror
1. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy | adventure | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-5::.
